An unidentified '''Drowned Priest''' is an unnamed minor character in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is played by guest star [[Jonathan Ryan]] and only appears in &quot;[[What is Dead May Never Die]].&quot; He is one of the [[Drowned Men]], priests who serve the [[Drowned God]] of the Iron Islands.

sections.Biography:
===[[Season 2]]===
[[File:TheonMeetsDrownedMan.jpg|thumb|Theon and Drowned Priest on the shore of Pyke in &quot;[[What is Dead May Never Die]]&quot;.]]
This Drowned Priest is the one who conducts the baptism of [[Theon Greyjoy]] after his return to [[Pyke (island)|Pyke]] and his decision to join [[Balon Greyjoy|his father]] in his [[War of the Five Kings|conquest]] of [[the North]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[What is Dead May Never Die]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
